OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy to start with outbreaks
OL,6,Fof light rain or drizzle. Cloud will
OL,7,Fclear from the east through the
OL,8,Fmorning, with afternoon sunny spells.
OL,9,FFresh winds, strengthening later.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FA bright evening, with plenty
OL,12,Fof late sunny spells. Mostly clear
OL,13,Fovernight, becoming rather cool in
OL,14,Frural parts. Fresh to strong winds.
OL,15,
OL,16,CWednesday:FA dry day with plenty of
OL,17,Fsunny spells, though tempered by the
OL,18,Fstrong easterly wind. Cooler near
OL,19,Fcoasts with a chance of gales.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
