OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:FLong
OL,6,Fsunny spells Thursday, but breezy.
OL,7,FWinds easing Friday and Saturday, with
OL,8,Fsunny intervals and a risk of showers.
OL,9,FTemperatures increasing, perhaps
OL,10,Fbecoming very warm.
